text: Robert Alan Labonte (born May 8, 1964) is a former American race car driver in the NASCAR Cup Series series. Labonte drove the #47 JTG Daugherty Racing Toyota Camry in 2011. From 1995 until 2005, Labonte drove the #18 car for Joe Gibbs Racing. In 2000 Labonte won the Sprint Cup championship with Joe Gibbs. == References == Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:American racecar drivers Category:NASCAR drivers Category:Sportspeople from Texas Category:People from Corpus Christi, Texas
